<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٧٣٩)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ نُصَيْبٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(الكامل المرفل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - وَلَقَدْ عَلِمْتَ وَلَسْتَ تَجْهَلُهُ ... أنَّ الْعَطَاءَ يَشِينُهُ الْمَطْلُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤٠)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَعْشى هَمْدَانَ:</span> <span class="c2">(السريع)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - أعْطِ الَّذِي أَعْطَيْتَه طَيِّباً ... لا خَيْرَ في الْمَنْكُودِ وَالنَّاكِدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢ - وَأَنْجِزِ الْوَعْدَ إِذَا قُلْتَهُ ... لَيْسَ الَّذِي يُنْجِزُ كَالْوَاعِدِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤١)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ دَاوُدُ بْنُ حَمَلٍ الْهَمْدَانِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ - وَبَعْضُ مَوَاعِد الأَقْوَامِ كَادَتْ ... تَكُونُ أَحَقَّ مِنْ دَيْنِ الْغَرِيمِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢ - فَوَعْدُكَ لا يُشِنْهُ الْمَطلُ إِنِّي ... رَأَيتُ الْمَطْلَ يَزْرِي بالْكَرِيمِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤٢)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الأَعْوَرُ الشَّنِّى:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١ - وَلَسْتُ بقَائِلٍ قَوْلاً لأَحْظَى ... بِوَعْدٍ لا يُصَدِّقُهُ فَعَالِي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٢ - وَلكِنِّي أُحَقِّقُهُ بِنُجْحٍ ... يُقَصِّرُ عِنْدَهُ عُمْرَ المِطَالِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>